  "detailed_description": "It's a VR action roguelike with a focus on melee combat and all kinds of abilities. Use more than just swords for fighting. Collect and use all kinds of abilities that can be activated with your gestures.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Randomly Generated Dungeons</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597210/extras/5c88fbb0f39294403a5f57311867572f.avif?t=1627920190\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>All dungeons are randomly generated with rooms filled with enemies, traps, and loot boxes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight With More Than Just Your Sword</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597210/extras/f6f72b6fd331b18ed0d18a9d93b5d7d6.avif?t=1627920190\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>The quick-access menu provides 4 slots to each hand for weapons and abilities.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597210/extras/0c7060f48aae3efb3fbb6647410c43c1.avif?t=1627920190\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br>Each weapon can carry 8 weapon abilities that can be triggered by gestures.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Get Stronger with New Powers and Better Weapons</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597210/extras/9b2a2669a02561e4007ef6c337a198fc.avif?t=1627920190\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597210/extras/6f6a283c39df195c402931cd82e617ee.avif?t=1627920190\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>Powers and weapons can be found in loot boxes and shops throughout the dungeons. In addition, randomly generated unique items grant you stats and abilities.",
  "about_the_game": "It's a VR action roguelike with a focus on melee combat and all kinds of abilities. Use more than just swords for fighting. Collect and use all kinds of abilities that can be activated with your gestures.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Randomly Generated Dungeons</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597210/extras/5c88fbb0f39294403a5f57311867572f.avif?t=1627920190\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>All dungeons are randomly generated with rooms filled with enemies, traps, and loot boxes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight With More Than Just Your Sword</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597210/extras/f6f72b6fd331b18ed0d18a9d93b5d7d6.avif?t=1627920190\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>The quick-access menu provides 4 slots to each hand for weapons and abilities.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597210/extras/0c7060f48aae3efb3fbb6647410c43c1.avif?t=1627920190\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br>Each weapon can carry 8 weapon abilities that can be triggered by gestures.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Get Stronger with New Powers and Better Weapons</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597210/extras/9b2a2669a02561e4007ef6c337a198fc.avif?t=1627920190\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1597210/extras/6f6a283c39df195c402931cd82e617ee.avif?t=1627920190\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>Powers and weapons can be found in loot boxes and shops throughout the dungeons. In addition, randomly generated unique items grant you stats and abilities.",
